  <entry>
    <title>hexo</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/04/15/hexo/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/04/15/hexo/</id>
    <published>2022-04-14T16:41:57.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-04-15T18:13:22.302Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装NodeJs"><a href="#安装NodeJs" class="headerlink" title="安装NodeJs"></a>安装NodeJs</h2><h3 id="检查是否安装完整"><a href="#检查是否安装完整" class="headerlink" title="检查是否安装完整"></a>检查是否安装完整</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装cnpm"><a href="#安装cnpm" class="headerlink" title="安装cnpm"></a>安装cnpm</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="初始化hexo"><a href="#初始化hexo" class="headerlink" title="初始化hexo"></a>初始化hexo</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="启动hexo"><a href="#启动hexo" class="headerlink" title="启动hexo"></a>启动hexo</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s #hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="编写文章"><a href="#编写文章" class="headerlink" title="编写文章"></a>编写文章</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n file # hexo new file</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>文件输出路径  <strong>.&#x2F;source&#x2F;_posts</strong></p></blockquote><h3 id="文件更新"><a href="#文件更新" class="headerlink" title="文件更新"></a>文件更新</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd 初始化hexo的文件夹</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g #hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="部署远程服务器"><a href="#部署远程服务器" class="headerlink" title="部署远程服务器"></a>部署远程服务器</h3><p><strong>新建仓库名称</strong> <code> 用户名.github.io</code></p><p><strong>安装插件</strong> <code>cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</code></p><p><strong>配置文件(_config.yml)</strong> </p><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Deployment</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">type:git</span><br><span class="line">repo:</span><br><span class="line">gitee: 仓库地址 </span><br><span class="line">github: 仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">branch:master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>同步服务器</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d # hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="更换主题"><a href="#更换主题" class="headerlink" title="更换主题"></a>更换主题</h3><p> <strong><a href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/24422335/answers/updated">主题地址</a></strong> </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd 项目目录</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia.git themes/yilia</span><br><span class="line">vim _config.yml</span><br><span class="line">theme:yilia</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;安装NodeJs&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#安装NodeJs&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;安装NodeJs&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;安装NodeJs&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&quot;检查是否安装完整&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#检查是否安装完整&quot; class=&quot;head</summary>
      
    
    
    
